{"tid":1741561,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"津巴布韋表示來自中國的援助遠低於北京所聲稱的金額，中國政府表達抗議。","createTime":"2019-11-20T11:36:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T12:21:34.000Z","uid":133680,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3ca5d271e1871c57eafa327128ebede50fc3404b","tid":1741561,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:36:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=370649&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D370649%26refer%3D&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLGo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=35a384f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D370649%26refer%3D&h=45eb6b63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=370649&amp;refer=</a><br />\n【Now新聞台】非洲國家津巴布韋公布財政數據，列出來自中國的援助遠低於北京所聲稱的金額，中國政府表達抗議。<br />\n<br />\n津巴布韋財政部長公布今年一月至九月財政數據，外國援助合共1億9400萬美元，主要盟友中國佔其中360萬美元，引起中國駐津巴布韋大使館批評，聲稱紀錄顯示一月至九月向津巴布韋提供多達1億3680萬美元援助，是津巴布韋政府所講的38倍，期望津巴布韋相關部門全面檢視援助數據，準確交代中方援助的實際情況。<br />\n<br />\n津巴布韋多年來倚靠中國經濟援助，包括發展供水和電力基建，目前面對嚴重旱災，經濟陷入危機，外匯、能源和藥物短缺。國際貨幣基金組織估計，當地直至今年8月，通脹達百分之300。<br />\n<br />\n據報津巴布韋曾經有官員私下侵吞外國金錢援助，有聲音要求當局調查是否有人將援助中飽私囊。"},{"pid":"c677d2f7465f13e369196a44fa788d6946c7518e","tid":1741561,"uid":165749,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:37:24.000Z","msg":"仲未認識國情，唔怪得佢"},{"pid":"0b89f73c686743ca64a5c11367079aa81cd5161a","tid":1741561,"uid":214502,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:39:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講個笑話 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ca1e9ce57ea33adef3f63db994b4d4b711d52d5","tid":1741561,"uid":249761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:40:01.000Z","msg":"香港人以前年年億億聲咁捐錢咪一樣<br />\n起埋啲爛鬼豆腐渣學校<br />\n隔兩年就冧"},{"pid":"a528c106b4ee2b5576a98ee721deead4cc70c7a8","tid":1741561,"uid":8441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:41:02.000Z","msg":"中間隔咗幾多個志平手套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c4af10f570dd51643d85f1b323b62408c0e302","tid":1741561,"uid":261697,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:47:22.000Z","msg":"肯定係有個無份食嘅出黎篤灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f617f7eedf579bb70b318a8e0a9df28948819a8b","tid":1741561,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:49:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c3f3b81c0ced6b4ab4d821d48b91ec93ff5925e","tid":1741561,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c677d2f7465f13e369196a44fa788d6946c7518e","tid":1741561,"uid":165749,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:37:24.000Z","msg":"仲未認識國情，唔怪得佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:50:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57486c5cb2650b50b1c8b9fca28b6755c548fa83","tid":1741561,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:51:54.000Z","msg":"又話用人仔取代美金<br />\n點解用美金嚟比人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b712c01e95412b4966cb06e9584129433207ad90","tid":1741561,"uid":312758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:54:12.000Z","msg":"維尼真係批左1億3680萬出黎<br />\n<br />\n但係扣埋車馬費<br />\n<br />\n360萬好過無啦"},{"pid":"58517541a63946385a99c5fb93e60cb8eb0aea6e","tid":1741561,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b712c01e95412b4966cb06e9584129433207ad90","tid":1741561,"uid":312758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"repl